approaches to analyze complex biological profiles made of DNA copy\nnumber and allele B frequencies. An R package implementing the approach will be\nmade available on github.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Oct 2017 15:08:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-13"}
